item_full_description: When you combine @puckytoys and @sanrio, you get ultimate cuteness! Watch out, 𝗣𝘂𝗰𝗸𝘆 𝘅 𝗦𝗮𝗻𝗿𝗶𝗼 𝗦𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗲𝘀 will be taking over your collection.
Come try out sweet pastries and aromatic coffee over at 𝗣𝗨𝗖𝗞𝗬 𝗥𝗮𝗯𝗯𝗶𝘁 𝗖𝗮𝗳𝗲 𝗦𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗲𝘀. PUCKY will make sure you’ll have a great time over at her café~
Take a trip down memory lane with 𝗗𝗶𝘀𝗻𝗲𝘆 𝗠𝗶𝗰𝗸𝗲𝘆 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝗙𝗿𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗱𝘀 𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗔𝗻𝗰𝗶𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝗧𝗶𝗺𝗲𝘀 𝗦𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗲𝘀. This retro series is a throwback to simpler times with our favorite Disney cuties.

Looks like Duckyo is not the only one hustlin’ hard.
Just like all of us, 𝗗𝘂𝗰𝗸𝘆𝗼 𝗙𝗿𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗱𝘀 𝗪𝗮𝗴𝗲 𝗘𝗮𝗿𝗻𝗲𝗿 𝗦𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗲𝘀 goes through different phases in adulting!
Presenting you 𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗠𝗼𝗻𝘀𝘁𝗲𝗿 𝗞𝗔𝗜𝗝𝗨 𝗦𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗲𝘀 - where you get to meet all kinds of kaiju, also known as giant monsters in Japanese! Which one is your favourite? Meet The Monsters in stores now~
Introducing the newest 𝗦𝗸𝘂𝗹𝗹𝗽𝗮𝗻𝗱𝗮 𝗪𝗮𝗿𝗺𝘁𝗵 𝗦𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗲𝘀 where she’s seen in a lighter, calmer and brighter shade!
In the city of night, everything is lit up by neon lights. Skullpanda is playing her part and keeping the night moving in the coolest way! 😎
